high_descs: Walk forward until the sink is to your right then go walk to the sink but stand slightly to the left of it.
Pick up the ice cream scoop to the left of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the end of the counter on your left then turn right and walk to the wall then turn left to face the table.
Put the ice cream scoop in the frying pan that's on the table in front of you.
Pick up the frying pan with the ice cream scoop in it.
Now walk over to the stove so you are in front of it facing it and turn left then take a step backwards.
Open the cabinet that's furthest to the right of the bank of cabinets in front of you and put the frying pan in it and close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a frying pan with an ice cream scoop in it in the cabinet.

high_descs: walk forwards a bit and hang a right to go over to the kitchen sink
grab a spoon off of the kitchen counter to the left of the sink
turn around and walk over to the kitchen table in the corner of the room
place the spoon inside of the sauce pan
pick up the sauce pan off of the kitchen table
turn around and walk over to the stove at the other end of the room
place the sauce pan in the cabinet to the bottom left of the stove
anns.task_desc: place a sauce pan with a spoon in it in the kitchen cabinet to the bottom left of the stove

high_descs: Move to the sink.
Pick up the spoon from the counter.
Bring the spoon to the white table.
Put the spoon in the black bowl on the right.
Pick up the bowl from the table.
Bring the bowl to the counter next to the stove.
Put the bowl in the bottom cabinet to the left of the stove.
anns.task_desc: Put the bowl with spoon into the bottom cabinet next to the stove.
